Comic Con Africa tickets go on sale today through Computicket. Ticket sales will consist of two launch phases, each with different pricing. Attendees who purchase tickets during Phase One will pay slightly less, although there is a limited number of tickets available. Phase One ticket sales open at 09:00, while Phase Two opens at 13:00. The ticket prices for each phase are listed below. Phase One – 09:00 Phase Two – 13:00 Once Phase One tickets are sold out, you will only be able to purchase tickets at Phase Two prices. Comic Con Africa will be held at the Kyalami International Convention Centre on 14-16 September 2018.